{"type":"message","id":"d5906dd7","parentId":"dfc91e67","timestamp":"2026-03-18T15:47:58.483Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，用户要我安装FFmpeg。让我安装FFmpeg来处理视频提取音频的任务。在Windows上，有几种方式安装FFmpeg：\n1. 使用chocolatey包管理器\n2. 直接下载FFmpeg二进制文件\n3. 使用winget\n\n让我尝试最简单的方法 - 直接下载FFmpeg并解压到系统路径。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"好的！我来安装FFmpeg并继续处理。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"exec:122","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 下载FFmpeg\n$ffmpegUrl = \"https://www.gyan.dev/ffmpeg/builds/ffmpeg-release-essentials.zip\"\n$outputPath = \"$env:TEMP\\ffmpeg.zip\"\n$extractPath = \"$env:LOCALAPPDATA\\ffmpeg\"\n\nWrite-Host \"正在下载FFmpeg...\" -ForegroundColor Cyan\nInvoke-WebRequest -Uri $ffmpegUrl -OutFile $outputPath -UseBasicParsing\n\nWrite-Host \"解压FFmpeg...\" -ForegroundColor Cyan\nExpand-Archive -Path $outputPath -DestinationPath $extractPath -Force\n\n# 找到ffmpeg.exe并添加到PATH\n$ffmpegExe = Get-ChildItem -Path $extractPath -Recurse -Filter \"ffmpeg.exe\" | Select-Object -First 1\nif ($ffmpegExe) {\n    $binPath = $ffmpegExe.Directory.FullName\n    [Environment]::SetEnvironmentVariable(\"Path\", $env:Path + \";\" + $binPath, \"User\")\n    Write-Host \"FFmpeg已安装到: $binPath\" -ForegroundColor Green\n    Write-Host \"请重新打开PowerShell以使用FFmpeg\" -ForegroundColor Yellow\n} else {\n    Write-Host \"未找到ffmpeg.exe\" -ForegroundColor Red\n}","workdir":"C:\\Users\\LWS\\.openclaw\\workspace","timeout":300}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"exec:123","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 检查是否已有FFmpeg\n$ffmpeg = Get-Command ffmpeg -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue\nif ($ffmpeg) {\n    Write-Host \"FFmpeg已安装: $($ffmpeg.Source)\" -ForegroundColor Green\n    & ffmpeg -version | Select-Object -First 1\n} else {\n    Write-Host \"FFmpeg未找到\" -ForegroundColor Red\n}","workdir":"C:\\Users\\LWS\\.openclaw\\workspace","timeout":10}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"exec:124","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 尝试使用Python的imageio-ffmpeg\nC:\\Python314\\pyt